∀ {R : Type u} [inst : CommRing R] [inst_1 : IsDomain R] {a : R}, Polynomial.X ^ 2 - Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C a ∣ Polynomial.X ^ 13 + Polynomial.X + 90 ↔ a = 2

∀ {R : Type u} [inst : CommRing R], ∀ (a : R), (Polynomial.X ^ 2 - Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C a) ∣ (Polynomial.X ^ 13 + Polynomial.X + 90) ↔ a = 2
∀ {R : Type u} [inst : CommRing R] (a : R), Polynomial.X ^ 2 - Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C a ∣ Polynomial.X ^ 13 + Polynomial.X + 90 → a = 2
